            <p>Let's explore how we can speed up your hiring process for [Data Analyst]. Are you free for a short call this week?</p>

            <p>Best,<br>{yourName}</p>`;
                                            break;

                                        case "insightDrivenRecruitment":
                                            subject = "Elevate Your Hiring Decisions for {hiringJobTitle} with AI-Powered Insights";
                                            templateContent = `<p>Dear {name},</p>

